data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Huge Price Reduction! You will love the Old Florida Charm of this quaint home located in Northwest Bradenton. This home has been meticulously and lovingly cared for and is not in a flood zone, no HOA, No CDD. Enjoy the sunshine, peacefulness and spaciousness of this huge lot - Property is over 1/3 of an acre and can be accessed by two streets - which makes it easy to bring your RV, Boats, Trailers and more! The two bedrooms are spacious with large, cedar lined closets, the bathrooms have had recent plumbing updates and complete remodels, the Kitchen has been completely remodeled and has new cabinets, granite countertops, new appliances and new flooring. Whole house fan. The mature trees, well irrigation, large lot and quiet neighborhood makes this house into a retreat. Newer Roof, Newer AC, Newer Hurricane windows, newer appliances. Close to Anna Maria Island, Blake Hospital, Robinson's Preserve and just down the street from the Warner Bayou Boat ramp. Make your appointment now to make this house your home.
